data.description: Brighton is a 72.4 acre, 115 unit single-family detached project located in northeast Tulare. Brighton features six floor plans ranging from 1,658 to 3,205 square feet on lots averaging 7,226 square feet. The community will include a park and a pond. Brighton, which is located north of East Cartmill Avenue and west of North Mooney Boulevard, is just over one mile east of Highway 99 giving quick access to major employers in the surrounding area. This neighborhood is expected to open in late July 2018.
